description:
Harford County 2017 Zoning Map.All official Zoning Maps shall be permanently
kept on file with the Harford County Council Administrator and a copy of the maps
shall be on file in the Department of Planning and Zoning. The maps

normal County business hours, and the Department of Planning and Zoning
shall provide for the sale of the maps to the general public.
